      passage: `<p>The Beirut Stock Exchange in Beirut, Lebanon, connects companies operating in Lebanon with potential investors. This is a valuable service since the time and expense necessary to find individual investors might otherwise be _____ for these companies: many of the companies could not operate if they had to do everything necessary to find investors for themselves.</p>`,
