      passage: `<p>Photographer M√°ria ≈Ývarbov√° has reached audiences well beyond her home country of Slovakia. In 2016, her work was featured at an international photography festival in _____ the exhibited photographs, with their vivid pastel colors, overexposed tones, and mirrorlike symmetry, captivated audiences.</p>`,
